div.p: Slots that clothing items can be placed into. Drag n' drop appropriate articles of clothing to their corresponding slots
Outfit layers can be created to express clothing layering.
- Use a jacket/flanel on top of a shirt
- Put socks and shoes on together
A valid outfit has 1 layer, and additonal layers are optional
